{"data":[{"date":"14:48 29/07","title":"HLV Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/hlv-barca-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ousmane Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/HLV-Ernesto-Valverde-phat-bieu-ve-Ousmane-Dembele-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh. Sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Grizmann v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca mua Malcom th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/dembele-muon-chay-tron-khoi-barca-180-191966.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ousmane Dembele mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/HLV-Ernesto-Valverde-phat-bieu-ve-Ousmane-Dembele-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ernesto Valverde tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Barca v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n\u00a0</span>Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Barca. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Dembele d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cDembele \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho Barca v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Dembele n\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Dembele c\u1ea3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1t cho m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i tin Dembele v\u00e0 Malcom s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1767","checkdouble":"192253"},{"date":"15:24 29/07","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zaha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Wilfried Zaha l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. C\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPalace d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn cho Zaha, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. \u1ede b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Zaha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, anh mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram: \u201cH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn mang t\u00ednh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n b\u1ecf theo d\u00f5i Crystal Palace tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zaha</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Wilfried Zaha, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea. The Blues nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard ra \u0111i. Pochettino c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/co-doi-bong-chi-40-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu-172-182476.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mua Zaha </span>\u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mua Zaha voi gia 40 trieu bang\" title=\"Tottenham mua Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/20/man-city-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Zaha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCrystal Palace t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Zaha \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song n\u1ebfu bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Zaha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Crystal Palace s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Palace b\u00e1n Zaha v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1766","checkdouble":"192254"},{"date":"14:56 29/07","title":"Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi t\u00e2n binh Barca ghi b\u00e0n ngay tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/hlv-valverde-noi-ve-man-ra-mat-cua-arthur.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Aston Villa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong b\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham quan t\u00e2m Grealish</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, Jack Grealish lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o, c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Grealish c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho Aston Villa. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft play-off l\u00ean Premier League ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-Grealish-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Grealish s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Aston Villa l\u1ea1i n\u1ed5i l\u00ean. Trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Man United, Liverpool v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Tottenham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Aston Villa g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Birmingham v\u00e0 tin ch\u1eafc s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Aston Villa quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa Nassef Sawaris c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Wes Edens c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c mua l\u1ea1i Aston Villa. T\u1ed5ng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 40 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng, con s\u1ed1 l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Sawaris v\u00e0 Edens l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u01a1m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 The Villa thanh to\u00e1n c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Aston Villa s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean U21 Anh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-ra-dieu-kien-mua-alderweireld-cho-mu-172-192150.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Tottenham, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-tai-ngo-modric-172-191894.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-khi-tottenham-quyet-dinh-dung-ngoai-ttcn-172-191864.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Tottenham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i TTCN?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1765","checkdouble":"192255"},{"date":"15:24 29/07","title":"Ander Herrera n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/ander-herrera-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-14-cua-mu-truoc-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd thu v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o trong 90 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Ander-Herrera-phat-bieu-ve-MU-sau-tran-thua-1-4-truoc-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, M.U \u0111\u1ec3 America c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i AC Milan.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-liverpool-tran-dau-icc-2018-dem-nay-372-192208.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U \u0111\u00e3 thua tan n\u00e1t 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span>. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 tung ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Sanchez, Herrera, Smalling... trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y M.U t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Herrera kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ander Herrera phat bieu ve MU\" title=\"Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/ander-herrera-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-14-cua-mu-truoc-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ander Herrera ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong m\u1ed7i hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTrong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan v\u00e0 Liverpool, h\u1ecd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi 16 ho\u1eb7c 17 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 10. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ed5 \u00edch sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 4 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1764","checkdouble":"192256"},{"date":"15:49 29/07","title":"Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Juventus.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Milan \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Higuain</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Juventus, Giuseppe Marotta x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1u quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd nghi\u00eam t\u00fac xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb g\u1eedi t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o m\u00e0 Bianconeri d\u00e0nh cho Chelsea v\u00e0 Milan trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-Higuain-cua-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nThe Blues chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Mirror c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Chelsea d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Higuain. L\u00fd do n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 120 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, The Blues c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Higuain t\u1ea1i b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri. Higuain t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y m\u00f9a 2015/16 t\u1ea1i Napoli. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A ch\u1ec9 sau 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Milan, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Higuain nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n. Sau nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i chi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Rossoneri gi\u1edd \u0111ang h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a UEFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Chelsea ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Higuain. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani. C\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Sarri khi \u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Empoli.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/drinkwater-muon-roi-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-192252.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-olivier-giroud-172-192243.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Olivier Giroud</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chelsea-bat-ngo-muon-so-huu-ngoi-sao-cua-arsenal-187-192241.html\">Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-ban-willian-cho-mu-172-192197.html\">N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n \u201ctr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng\u201d Mourinho cho M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1763","checkdouble":"192257"},{"date":"16:22 29/07","title":"Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua sao h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Aston Villa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong b\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham quan t\u00e2m Grealish</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, Jack Grealish lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o, c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Grealish c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho Aston Villa. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111\u00e1 chung k\u1ebft play-off l\u00ean Premier League ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-Grealish-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Grealish s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Aston Villa l\u1ea1i n\u1ed5i l\u00ean. Trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Man United, Liverpool v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Tottenham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Aston Villa g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Birmingham v\u00e0 tin ch\u1eafc s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Aston Villa quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa Nassef Sawaris c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Wes Edens c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c mua l\u1ea1i Aston Villa. T\u1ed5ng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00ean t\u1edbi 40 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng, con s\u1ed1 l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Sawaris v\u00e0 Edens l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u01a1m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 The Villa thanh to\u00e1n c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Aston Villa s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean U21 Anh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-ra-dieu-kien-mua-alderweireld-cho-mu-172-192150.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Tottenham, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-tai-ngo-modric-172-191894.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-khi-tottenham-quyet-dinh-dung-ngoai-ttcn-172-191864.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Tottenham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i TTCN?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1762","checkdouble":"192258"},{"date":"15:24 29/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 29/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/28/Alaves-vs-Real-Madrid-(21h15-ngay-2910)-Cho-BBC-bung-no-tro-lai-hinh-anh-goc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 29/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec Isco, Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2907 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2907 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2907-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard v\u00ec Isco</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo AS, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Isco th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-khong-muon-mua-hazard-180-192194.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2907-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-khong-muon-mua-hazard-180-192194.html\">Real ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Hazard</span><br>\r\nReal kh\u00f4ng mua Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea b\u1edfi gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. Ch\u00ednh HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Real Madrid s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111i tu nghi\u1ec7p&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real s\u1eafp cho Sociedad m\u01b0\u1ee3n Theo Hernandez. Sau khi ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real v\u1ee5 Edinson Cavani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani\" title=\"Cavani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/tho-world-cup-tu-ket-bi-braxin.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real Madrid mua Edinson Cavani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu Los Blancos chi ra 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Jordan Pickford</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford c\u1ee7a Everton, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Thibaut Courtois.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-45-trieu-bang-mua-pickford-172-192184.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/chelsea-chot-45-trieu-bang-mua-pickford.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-45-trieu-bang-mua-pickford-172-192184.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span><br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd mua Jordan Pickford c\u1ee7a Everton trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 107 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos. Hi\u1ec7n hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u0110V Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n Harry Kane thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t t\u1eeb Marca, c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Harry Kane thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo trong vai tr\u00f2 trung phong s\u0103n b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Keylor Navas, d\u00f9 s\u1eafp mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Thibaut Courtois song Los Blancos v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Benzema l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chia tay Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema\" title=\"Benzema\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/benzema-len-tieng-chot-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Benzema tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Benzema kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dortmund ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao cho Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dortmund kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Christian Pulisic cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1761","checkdouble":"192259"},{"date":"17:50 29/07","title":"Mourinho: \"\u0110\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, Sanchez kh\u00f4ng t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea1\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/mourinho-da-voi-cac-dong-doi-the-nay-sanchez-khong-tuc-moi-la-la.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sanchez sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua cay \u0111\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Man United thua \u0111\u1eadm Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu ICC \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u00edt \u1ecfi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLukaku v\u00e0 Rashford v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Martial c\u0169ng r\u1eddi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee9a con m\u1edbi sinh. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Sanchez l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU.</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ef1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef c\u1ee7a Sanchez\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez gi\u1eadn d\u1eef v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sanchez gi\u1eadn d\u1eef v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Mourinho l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/mourinho-da-voi-cac-dong-doi-the-nay-sanchez-khong-tuc-moi-la-la.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sanchez gi\u1eadn d\u1eef \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh gi\u1eadn d\u1eef c\u1ee7a Sanchez \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed u \u00e1m trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Man United v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Sanchez th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00e1c b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh \u01b0? Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSanchez l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1eadn d\u1eef ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o ch\u01a1i 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng CLB. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ander-herrera-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-14-cua-mu-truoc-liverpool-172-192256.html\">Ander Herrera n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khong-hai-long-voi-bld-mu-ve-ke-hoach-mua-sam-172-192248.html\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110 MU v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1760","checkdouble":"192260"},{"date":"17:09 29/07","title":"Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng lo m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/navas-khong-lo-mat-suat-da-chinh-tai-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u00e0o tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Chelsea.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Courtois</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0<br>\r\nKeylor Navas chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid t\u1eeb Levante v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1986 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i thay th\u1ebf anh v\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015, \u0111\u00fang ra Real \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 David de Gea n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 m\u00e1y fax kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. Sau nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Man United, Los Blancos chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng quan t\u00e2m sang Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Sau khi Courtois t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/navas-khong-lo-mat-suat-da-chinh-tai-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Navas kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui\u201d, Navas n\u00f3i v\u1edbi La Nacion. \u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u1ed5n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00e2m tr\u00ed v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc. R\u1ed3i ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. T\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea1i Madrid. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m qua \u0111i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac l\u1edbn lao.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n Ch\u00faa v\u00ec c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e2ng l\u00e2ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed t\u1ea1i Madrid.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2907-180-192259.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 29/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-sap-cho-sociedad-muon-theo-hernandez-180-192199.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111i tu nghi\u1ec7p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-khong-muon-mua-hazard-180-192194.html\">Real ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/psg-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-edinson-cavani-180-192189.html\">PSG c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real v\u1ee5 Edinson Cavani</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pepe-duoc-porto-va-wolves-quan-tam-180-192183.html\">35 tu\u1ed5i, c\u1ef1u sao Real v\u1eabn h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean TTCN</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1759","checkdouble":"192261"},{"date":"17:40 29/07","title":"David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/29/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 xem x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Silva c\u00f9ng TBN tr\u1ea3i qua th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a David Silva \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG gi\u00e0nh 3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp bao g\u1ed3m World Cup 2010, Euro 2008 v\u00e0 2012.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Silva c\u00f9ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, La Roja \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/David-Silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Silva tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc gian kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, Silva \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. T\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017, anh c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eadt s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1ng cho c\u1eadu con trai Mateo b\u1ecb sinh non.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Silva tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Man City sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve David Silva\" title=\"tien ve David Silva\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau World Cup, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung 100% cho con trai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, t\u1edd Mirror tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Silva. \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Manchester v\u00e0o ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha hay kh\u00f4ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Manchester. T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed t\u00f4i l\u00e0 con trai, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd tham kh\u1ea3o vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, bao g\u1ed3m HLV Pep Guardiola, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, Silva \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 125 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110TQG cao th\u1ee9 6 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mata-muon-tro-lai-dt-tay-ban-nha-172-191959.html\">Sao M.U m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/enrique-can-giup-dt-tay-ban-nha-vo-dich-euro-2020-184-191881.html\">Enrique c\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\">Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1758","checkdouble":"192262"},{"date":"10:30 29/07","title":"MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-mina-len-35-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca, theo The Sun, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, HLV Jose Mouirnho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/MU-quyet-tam-mua-Yerry-Mina-cua-Barca-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU \u0111ang th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Leicester h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 Magui 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Spurs \u0111\u00f2i 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Maguire v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Alderweireld, song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng \u00e2m th\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, M.U quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Colombia. Everton c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mina, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, M.U v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Mina l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-vuot-mat-everton-vu-yerry-mina-172-192153.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca</span>, theo The Sun, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU nang gia hoi mua Mina len 35 trieu bang\" title=\"MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Mina l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-mina-len-35-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Mina l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m94 c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, Mina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Eric Bailly h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn th\u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 M.U chi ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Barca h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t thay v\u00ec cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap M.U t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\u00a0chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1757","checkdouble":"192242"},{"date":"10:48 29/07","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Olivier Giroud","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-olivier-giroud.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud c\u1ee7a Chelsea, theo RMC Sport, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ligue 1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giroud kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Chelsea b\u1ecf ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud t\u1eeb Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Conte, song t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn khi Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-olivier-giroud.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giroud b\u1ecb HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Olivier Giroud \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Gonzalo Higuain, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Higuain, The Blues chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Giroud g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. The Blues s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea-172-191744.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Giroud</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Marseille gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Giroud</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua Olivier Giroud c\u1ee7a Chelsea, theo RMC Sport, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ligue 1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Giroud\" title=\"Giroud\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/Atletico-muon-co-Giroud-trong-mua-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0Marseille mu\u1ed1n mua\u00a0</span>Giroud v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mario Balotelli c\u1ee7a Nice, song qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 quan t\u00e2m m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Giroud.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Marseille c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Giroud y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho anh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marseille mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Giroud l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiroud s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32, b\u1edfi v\u1eady tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Atletico Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1756","checkdouble":"192243"},{"date":"10:48 29/07","title":"Chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Watford mu\u1ed1n \u201cr\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\u201d Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/12/10/chi-18-trieu-bang-watford-muon-rut-ruot-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Watford mu\u1ed1n mua Divock Origi c\u1ee7a Liverpool, theo Miror, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Vicarage Road ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Origi kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Divock Origi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Wolfsburg theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi 6 b\u00e0n sau 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Watford mu\u1ed1n mua Divock Origi  v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Watford mu\u1ed1n mua Divock Origi  v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/7/Watford-muon-mua-Divock-Origi--voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Origi r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Anfield \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 cao, \u201cS\u00f3i xanh\u201d \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Hi\u1ec7n Origi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng Liverpool, anh \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDivock Origi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Roberto Firmino, Daniel Sturridge, Danny Ings v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 sao tr\u1ebb Solanke n\u1eefa, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Origi \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Origi c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Watford chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t cho Origi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Watford mu\u1ed1n mua Divock Origi c\u1ee7a Liverpool, theo Miror, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Vicarage Road ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Divock Origi dang co nhung buoc tien lon tai Liverpool\" title=\"Divock Origi \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/12/10/ga-son-cua-liverpool-da-tu-choi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Watford mu\u1ed1n chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Divock Origi\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Watford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Origi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Origi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Watford mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Vicarage Road c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n d\u00e0nh cho Origi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i cho Watford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Origi, Danny Ings c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi Liverpool. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-danny-ings-172-192178.html\" target=\"_blank\">Crystal Palace mu\u1ed1n chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ings</span>, Southampton c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1755","checkdouble":"192244"},{"date":"11:02 29/07","title":"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t ch\u1ecdn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n U19 Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/29/cau-thu-tre-goc-viet-chon-khoac-ao-tuyen-u19-trung-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t Nam Li Tenglong (hay L\u00ea \u0110\u1eb1ng Long, t\u00ean g\u1ecdi Vi\u1ec7t Nam) \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn U19 Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 n\u01a1i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u1edd Sport Sina d\u1eabn l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t Nam Li Tenglong (L\u00ea \u0110\u1eb1ng Long), m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc thu\u1ed9c H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 CSKA Moskva: \u201cT\u00f4i sinh ra \u1edf Nga, nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 World Cup\u201d.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSinh n\u0103m 2001, Li Tenglong \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao 1,8 m. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea1t sang bi\u00ean. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Li Tenglong l\u1ecdt \"m\u1eaft xanh\" c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Serie A l\u00e0 AC Milan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t Li Tenglong ch\u1ecdn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n U19 Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t Li Tenglong ch\u1ecdn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n U19 Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/anh3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Li Tenglong l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a AC Milan, c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Serie A, Italy.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 17, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Li Tenglong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 50.000 euro tr\u00ean trang chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Transfermarkt v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2017. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y cao g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (2/2017) v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng (12/2017).\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nLi Tenglong c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam, m\u1eb9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Trung Qu\u1ed1c, nh\u01b0ng sinh ra v\u00e0 l\u1edbn l\u00ean t\u1ea1i Nga. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a m\u1ed9t trong ba \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong 3 qu\u1ed1c gia (Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Nga v\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c), cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Li Tenglong quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn Trung Qu\u1ed1c, qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1eb9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia sau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U19 Trung Qu\u1ed1c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 Weifang Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u quy t\u1ee5 12 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1/8 t\u1edbi. Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Trung Qu\u1ed1c n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Spartak Moskva (Nga), U19 Espanyol (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) v\u00e0 U19 Santos Languna (Mexico).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Li Tenglong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a FIFA, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, th\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \"nh\u1ea3y\" sang \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa (Brazil/T\u00e2y Ban Nha). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Zing.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1754","checkdouble":"192245"},{"date":"07:19 29/07","title":"Sao Man City: \u201cPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Pogba khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia ph\u1ea3i im m\u1ed3m\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/sao-man-city-phong-do-cua-pogba-khien-cac-chuyen-gia-phai-im-mom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i CLB, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Benjamin Mendy ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMendy ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft h\u00e2n hoan sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 trong v\u00f2ng 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng Mendy v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadp tan m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Pogba tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0u m\u00e8, t\u00f4 v\u1ebd, m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Les Bleus gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Mendy cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 Paul Pogba v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c hay g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00ec v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Benjamin Mendy ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Benjamin Mendy ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/mendy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Benjamin Mendy ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Juventus, ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Claudio Marchisio v\u00e0 Andrea Pirlo, \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u1edf Man United v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Paul Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda l\u1edbn cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft, t\u1eebng chung m\u00e0u \u00e1o Le Havre, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Pogba t\u1ea1i \u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1, \u0111\u00f4i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, kho\u1ea3ng 13-14 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 gi\u1edd n\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Manchester, Premier League v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, anh \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a Paul, anh \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo; &ndash; Benjamin Mendy ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-duoc-loi-de-nghi-133-trieu-bang-anh-cho-pogba-172-192088.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/mu-nhan-duoc-loi-de-nghi-133-trieu-bang-anh-cho-pogba.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-duoc-loi-de-nghi-133-trieu-bang-anh-cho-pogba-172-192088.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 133 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho Pogba</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd The Sun c\u1ee7a Anh, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 133 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 CLB Juventus.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-chi-trich-pogba-choi-bong-khong-nao-172-192013.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/huyen-thoai-mu-chi-trich-pogba-choi-bong-khong-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-chi-trich-pogba-choi-bong-khong-nao-172-192013.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Pogba ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o</span><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra ho\u00e0i nghi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Paul Pogba trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man Utd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh phong \u0111\u1ed9 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/bayern-munich-vs-man-city-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192209.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/bayern-munich-vs-man-city-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/bayern-munich-vs-man-city-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192209.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Bayern Munich 2-2 Man City (H2): D\u00e0n sao tr\u1ebb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs Man City: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Bayern Munich tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1753","checkdouble":"192231"}]}